Package Shop

Class Summary
ColorController ColorController delivers a newly produced color into the print shop
ColorFrame ColorFrame displays the input frame where the user selects sequences of colors to print lines of text.
OutputFrame OutputFrame displays the lines of colored output text.
PrintShop PrintShop assembles colors and text lines into colored text
Start Start assembles the components of the print shop and starts it.
TextController TextController delivers lines of text to the print shop
TextFrame TextFrame displays the input view where a user types lines of text to print
